title: How to Reprogram Your Personality
itunes:title: How to Reprogram Your Personality
description:
You are not who you think you are. In fact, you can stop being who you always have been and be anyone that you want to be starting right now! In this episode, I am going to talk about how to reprogram yourself into the person that you have always truly wanted to be.
